      ],
      "description": "### Deskripsi\n\nREST API sederhana untuk mengelola device IoT dan telemetry.\n\nBase URL:\n\nhttp://localhost:8000/api/v1\n\nTidak perlu token atau API key.\n\n### Endpoint utama\n\n| Method | Endpoint | Deskripsi |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| POST | /devices | Membuat device baru. |\n| GET | /devices?page=1&limit=10 | Mengambil daftar device dengan pagination. |\n| GET | /devices/{device_id} | Mengambil detail device berdasarkan UUID. |\n| PUT | /devices/{device_id} | Update semua field device. |\n| PATCH | /devices/{device_id} | Update sebagian field device. |\n| DELETE | /devices/{device_id} | Menghapus device. |\n| POST | /devices/{device_id}/telemetry | Membuat telemetry untuk device ke Cassandra. |\n| GET | /devices/{device_id}/telemetry?start_month=2026-01&end_month=2026-12 | Mengambil telemetry device dari Cassandra. |\n| GET | /devices/{device_id}/telemetry/latest | Mengambil telemetry terbaru. |\n\nCatatan:\n\n- device_id memakai UUID.\n- Device disimpan di PostgreSQL.\n- Telemetry disimpan di Cassandra table device_telemetries."
    },
    {
      "name": "Telemetry",
      "item": [
        {
